{"tid":2198723,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"武肺病毒最新簡略資訊","createTime":"2020-09-11T14:26:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T05:07:42.000Z","uid":38861,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"cfc92cc190ddb78417f1bdddd96f90414792c4a1","tid":2198723,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:26:36.000Z","msg":"習大大在中國舉行武肺表揚大會之際，有科學家最近亦發現到(Ref1)，武肺病毒至少會在人體裡頭產生23種現今未知其功能的蛋白質，部份蛋白質為首次發現，而其餘的就是已知蛋白質的加長或者縮短版本。<br />\n<br />\n能否透過針對研究所發現的蛋白質來抑制武肺生長，至今還是未知之數。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而近日亦有科學家整理武肺病毒基因的排組並加以分析(Ref2)，得出武肺病毒進入美國境內的兩大途徑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YeEiUDa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYeEiUDa.jpg&h=8c643e37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1.由中國直抵華盛頓。<br />\n<br />\n2.中國直送意大利，再由意大利送到紐約。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而有一點略為令人擔心的是，美國內華達州（Nevada)在八月尾出現武肺再度感染個案。(Ref3)<br />\n<br />\n香港再度感染的患者並無出現病徵，但美國這位病人卻出現比第一次感染更嚴重的症狀。<br />\n<br />\n這位美國病人到底是否只是個別例子，日後陸續出現的再度感染個案自會揭曉。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2739-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41586-020-2739-1&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=77c67e9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.nature.com/articles/s41586-020-2739-1</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2020/09/09/science.abc8169?rss=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscience.sciencemag.org%2Fcontent%2Fearly%2F2020%2F09%2F09%2Fscience.abc8169%3Frss%3D1&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=f3d6ea7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://science.sciencemag.org/content/early/2020/09/09/science.abc8169?rss=1</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=3680955\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpapers.ssrn.com%2Fsol3%2Fpapers.cfm%3Fabstract_id%3D3680955&d=lPOaXpfFeUboYNX3auI3fnQc4T2II2f942UkEibGql8%3D&h=322f608c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=3680955</a>"},{"pid":"fbf99d432ec25d512d54ec02d287e6ea4bd429e7","tid":2198723,"uid":364233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:27:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd757f4a463991781bca725717039f26502e158f","tid":2198723,"uid":73855,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:27:50.000Z","msg":"正評"},{"pid":"b81e95d4bb4f4791232d29b3b07c6dd80fb0e639","tid":2198723,"uid":199689,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:27:59.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"3153a3af60a38fe2efd604de68d218ea6238f297","tid":2198723,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:28:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"d1affa7e9aab3ee78d990f82c7eac7bbb853d147","tid":2198723,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻武肺去完歐洲後係咪弱左？"},{"pid":"e98ace6d018bb8ea95fe2066a0d5b377463b135d","tid":2198723,"uid":38861,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d1affa7e9aab3ee78d990f82c7eac7bbb853d147","tid":2198723,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:28:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />隻武肺去完歐洲後係咪弱左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-11T14:31:53.000Z","msg":"無任何科學根據能夠證明。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上現今主流的D614G變種究竟會唔會令死亡率提高，暫時都無任何文獻能夠指出得到，只係知隻變種病毒會更容易入侵細胞。<br />\n<br />\n但更容易入侵細胞會唔會令到死亡率增加，兩者現時無科學根據可以證實。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6df0982f6c20f8d1d98519725ab0942759765e3e","tid":2198723,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"e98ace6d018bb8ea95fe2066a0d5b377463b135d","tid":2198723,"uid":38861,"like":1,"d